This paper focuses on usability and user experience issues in open source software development, which are closely related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and software engineering (cs.SE). The study also involves analyzing online discussions and collaboration within OSS communities, which could fall under cyber security (cs.CYBER), social and information networks (cs.SI), and software development (cs.SD).
